parameters: \n< Serena >.......

\n< Serena >......It's so quiet here. I've never seen a
brothel like this before.

\n< Serena >I was truly fed up with the noise in this
establishment, but now that I've been invited, it
feels strange...

\n< Deacon >Who's there? Wait, isn't that Ginny! Hey you!
Where the hell have you been wandering around!?
\n< Serena >Deacon, are you safe?

\n< Serena >There were various things... and now I have
finally returned. However, this is...

\n< Deacon >Ah, you heard too, right? Madame, she got fucking
killed.

\n< Deacon >Well, she certainly had made enemies everywhere...
but to be killed in such a way...
\n< Serena >Did you see it? What happened?

\n< Deacon >I didn't see the moment she was killed. Not just
me, nobody saw it.

\n< Deacon >Do your job as usual. It's closing time. Madame
hasn't come out of her room at all, right?

\n< Deacon >I had a strange feeling, so I opened the door...
hehe. Blood and flesh were scattered all over the
room... It looked like a stew that had been
thoroughly mixed.
\n< Serena >Tha...t was...

\n< Serena >Such a gruesome way to be killed... Did no one
notice?

\n< Deacon >At least I didn't notice. The other whores ran
away immediately.

\n< Deacon >I ran away too, you know. If the city police find
me, they'll treat me as the culprit without
question and hang me.

\n< Serena >Then why are you here now? The city police are
still searching for the culprit.
\n< Deacon >Ganuron-sama will support me.

\n< Deacon >Ganuron-sama will support me. And you too, right?
The fact that we're here like this...

\n< Deacon >Hehe, I'll protect you from the city police, so
reopen the brothel. I'm grateful to the point of
tears... damn it.
\n< Serena >.......

\n< Deacon >Are you planning to turn this place into a
branch...? We finally crushed the competition. We
should just do as we please in the slums.

\n< Deacon >Anyway, we'll reopen the brothel. Only the second
floor though.

\n< Deacon >Ah, so busy, so busy. Gotta greet people, make
arrangements, and get the business back up and
running...
\n< Serena >Ah.......
\n< Serena >.......
\n< Serena >It's the door to the hall.
\n< Serena >I doubt I'll pass through here anymore...
売春状況
２０～２９：通常売春
